data.text:
Congratulations to the SHS swim teams who participated in the State Tournament at BYU last weekend. The Boys team took 4th overall and the Girls team placed 7th. The following result were from finals on Saturday

Girls Medley Relay - 4th (Brinley Weight, Kate Brower, Macie Poulson, Ella Brimhall)

Boys Medley Relay - 3rd **SHS School Record 1:37.88 (Nate Anderson, Nick Oman, George Holm, Easton Mousser)

Macie Poulson - 10th in 200 Free and 7th in 500 Free

Easton Mousser - 4th in 200 Free and 3rd in 500 Free

Kate Brower - 7th in both 200 IM and 100 Breast

Brinley Weight - 13th in 100 Fly and 7th in 100 Back ** SHS School Record :59.96

George Holm - 11th in 100 Butterfly

Nick Oman - 5th in 100 Breast **SHS School Record :58.02

Nate Anderson - 8th in 500 Free and 9th in 100 Back

Girls 200 Free Relay - 11th (Colbie Weight, Haylee Hatfield, Sophie Mottishaw, Ella Brimhall)

Boys 200 Free Relay - 7th (Nick Oman, Jon Ferrin, John Paapke, Josh Gee)

Girls 400 Free Relay - 7th (Macie Poulson, Colbie Weight, Brinley Weight, Kate Brower)
